links.label: Viva Engage Groups Activity Group Detail

params.markdown:
This dashboard gives a clear view of your organization’s entra ID users.
It includes:
- Key metrics like on_premises_provisioning_errors, property_causing_error.
- Detailed analysis on risk level, risk state and risk error
- Information on user details like user upn, user types

It helps you easily monitor and analyze risks involved.

[**Integrations Page**](/app/integrations/detail/o365_metrics/overview)
